LIBERTIES UNION; CIVIL RIGHTS VIOLATIONS; EVICTIONS; LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICERS; 
MEETINGS; POLICE ESPIONAGE; LONG, RICHARD; NEWPORT BEACH POLICE DEPARTMENT; 
