island of Hawaii, left, the 82nd one destroyed during the current eruption. The 
house in the Kalapana Gardens subdivision was ignited less than 12 hours after 
another home a short distance away burned. The flow continued moving toward 
other dwellings, authorities said. Associated Press 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
