<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE: OLAJUWON FINED FOR FIGHTING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The NBA fined six players for fighting Thursday, including Houston center Akeem 
Olajuwon, who was assessed $5,000 for pushing Sacramento's Greg Kite in the 
face. 
</P>
<P>
Jerry Reynolds of Orlando was fined $3,500 for an altercation with Detroit's 
Bill Laimbeer; Laimbeer was fined $750 for a flagrant foul on Reynolds, and 
James Edwards, Scott Hastings and William Bedford of Detroit were each fined 
$500 for leaving the bench area. 
</P>
</TEXT>
