and nearby hotels of spraying in the area. ; Photo, A group of malathion foes 
gathered around Disneyland-area hotels Thursday night to warn visitors of the 
spraying. They picketed the Anaheim Hilton and Towers, top picture, and the 
Marriott, walking from one location to another. KIM D. JOHNSON / Los Angeles 
Times 
</P>
