</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Many of the top swimmers in the Southern Section will compete Saturday in the 
Foothill Swim Games and the Mission Viejo invitational. 
</P>
<P>
The Foothill meet, which begins at 9 a.m. at Foothill High School, features 21 
teams, most of them from Orange County. The top boys' teams include Capistrano 
Valley, El Toro, Fountain Valley, Marina and Villa Park. The top girls' teams 
will be El Toro, Foothill, Fountain Valley and Los Alamitos. 
</P>
<P>
The Mission Viejo meet will be at the Marguerite Recreation Center, with finals 
scheduled to start at 2 p.m. Saturday. 
