<P>
JANET JACKSON TICKETS GO ON SALE SUNDAY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Tickets for Janet Jackson's June 23 and 24 stand at the Pacific Amphitheatre go 
on sale Sunday at 9 a.m. at the amphitheater box office, Ticketron outlets, and 
via Teletron. Outlets will distribute priority wristbands starting at 7 a.m. 
</P>
<P>
Tickets go on sale Saturday at 10 a.m. for Pacific shows on May 26 by Tracy 
Chapman and Johnny Clegg &amp; Savuka and July 7 by UB40. Information: (714) 
634-1300. 
</P>
