<TEXT>
<P>
Ronnie Daigrepont, a jockey injured in a spill at Jefferson Downs, remained in 
critical condition in a coma today at St. Jude Hospital. 
</P>
<P>
Daigrepont, 21, of Kenner was headed into the homestretch Wednesday night 
aboard Tudor Gold when his horse and another apparently clipped hoofs. 
</P>
<P>
